text: Alexandria is a city in the state of Louisiana. It it the largest city in the Central Louisiana region, ninth-largest in the state and parish seat of Rapides Parish. Alexandria was incorporated in 1818. In 2020, about 45,000 people lived there. ==References== ==Other websites== Category:Cities in Louisiana Category:Parish seats in Louisiana Category:Settlements in Rapides Parish, Louisiana Category:1818 establishments in the United States Category:1810s establishments in Louisiana
